OL,7,FTwo men have been banned from driving
OL,8,Fafter injuring a taxi driver while
OL,9,Fracing down a dual carriageway in
OL,10,FMagor.
OL,12,FThe pair from Newport have been banned
OL,13,Ffrom driving for two years.
OL,15,FThe two men, aged 21 and 22, caused a
OL,16,Fcollision on 16 October 2022 during an
OL,17,Fillegal car meet on the A4810 near
OL,18,FMagor.
