OL,7,FOfficers were called to reports of a
OL,8,Fthree-car collision between a grey
OL,9,FSkoda, a black Vauxhall Corsa and a
OL,10,Fwhite Volkswagen Polo.
OL,12,FThe taxi was not involved in the
OL,13,Fearlier race.
OL,15,FBoth men appeared for sentencing
OL,16,Fbefore Cardiff Crown Court on Monday
OL,17,F29 July after pleading guilty to
OL,18,Fcausing serious injury by dangerous
OL,19,Fdriving.
