OL,7,FThe officer in the case, PC Matthew
OL,8,FDavies, said the incident could have
OL,9,Fbeen a lot worse.
OL,11,F"It is more through luck than
OL,12,Fjudgement that the resulting injuries
OL,13,Fcaused by these two defendants was not
OL,14,Fmore severe; there can be no excuses
OL,15,Ffor deciding to drive as dangerously
OL,16,Fas this.
