OL,7,F"The victim in this case will live
OL,8,Fwith the impact of their reckless
OL,9,Fdecisions for many years to come, and
OL,10,Four thoughts remain with them as they
OL,11,Frecover from the serious injuries
OL,12,Fsustained in the collision.
OL,14,F"Let this case be a reminder to
OL,15,Feveryone who gets behind the wheel -
OL,16,Fplease think before you drive.
